    "dtir Hendersoneiile Ntwi Established in 1894 Hendersonville Times Established in 1881 Published every afternoon except Sunday at 227 North Main Street Hendersonville N C by The TimesNews Co Inc Owner and Publisher J T FAIN C M OGLE HENRY ATKIN Editor Managing Editor _ City Editor SUBSCRIPTION RATES By TimesNews Carrier in Hendersonville or else where per week 12c Due to hirh postage rates the subscription price of The TimesNews in tones above No 2 will be based on the cost of postage Entered as second class matter at the post office in Hendersonville N C TELEPHONE 87 THURSDAY FEBRUARY 4 1937 BIBLE THOUGHT THE SHEPHERD PSALM 10 My cup runneth over Ps 235 ilad and festal moments come to the saddest and most weary hearts At such times life seems to us like a chalice mixed by the loving hand of iod and overflowing with His mercy and loving kindness The mouth is filled with laughter and the tongue with singing then we say among the heathen The Lord hath done great things for us whereof we are glad Ps 12623 To be continued THEY MADE RECORD TO BE PROUD OF The men and women of Asheville and Hendersonville"
